---

<BaseLayout
  title="Zipminator - Quantum-Safe Cybersecurity Solution"
  description="The next generation of cybersecurity, combining Quantum Key Distribution with NIST Post-Quantum Encryption standards for unbreakable protection."
>
  <!-- Sticky Beta CTA - Shows after scrolling past hero -->
