        <p class="text-lg text-base-300 max-w-3xl mb-12">
          IBM 127-qubit quantum hardware + NIST FIPS 203 ML-KEM-768 post-quantum encryption. The first installable quantum security platform.
        </p>

        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
          <a href="#pricing" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 text-lg font-semibold text-white bg-primary-600 hover:bg-primary-700 rounded-lg transition shadow-lg shadow-primary-500/50">
